The evidence with the title 'Walmart family wealth is equal to bottom 42% of Americans ... ' says Dec 20, 2013  ... The Walton family , which owns Wal-Mart, controls a fortune equal to the wealth of the bottom 42 % of Americans combined.  ... In 2010 the wealth of six Walton family heirs was $ 89.5 billion , 22 percent higher than in 2007. 
